				 Gnome2::Wnck
				--------------

This module allows you to use the Window Navigator Construction Kit library
(libwnck for short) from Perl.

The index of the automatically generated API documentation can be accessed
with:

  perldoc Gnome2::Wnck::index

				 Installation
				--------------

To install Gnome2::Wnck run the following commands:

  perl Makefile.PL
  make
  make test
  make install

				 Dependencies
				--------------

Gnome2::Wnck depends on:

  ExtUtils::Depends >= 0.20
  ExtUtils::PkgConfig >= 1.03
  Glib >= 1.04
  Gtk2 >= 1.00
  libwnck >= 2.20.0

If you need support for libwnck < 2.20.0, use Gnome2::Wnck 0.14.
